      "updated": 1749000000005,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PaymentService\n(orchestrator)\n─────────────\nfixed Charge order:\n1  idempotency check\n2  validate token\n3  fraud score\n4  authorize (bank)\n5  persist payment\n6  write ledger\n7  store idem LAST\n8  notify webhook\n─────────────\nthe 3 invariants:\n• exactly-once\n• version CAS\n• debits = credits",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "svc",
      "originalText": "PaymentService\n(orchestrator)\n─────────────\nfixed Charge order:\n1  idempotency check\n2  validate token\n3  fraud score\n4  authorize (bank)\n5  persist payment\n6  write ledger\n7  store idem LAST\n8  notify webhook\n─────────────\nthe 3 invariants:\n• exactly-once\n• version CAS\n• debits = credits",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a4",
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
